quran[5{c,v,t}:
13,1,"a l- meem ray yeh kitaab Ellahi ki ayaat hain, aur jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai woh ain haq hai, magar ( tumhari qoum ke ) aksar log maan nahi rahay hain"
13,2,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne asmano ko aisay saharon ke baghair qaim kya jo tum ko nazar atay ho n, phir woh apne takhat saltanat par jalva farma howa, aur uss ne aftaab o Mahtab ko aik qanoon ka paband banaya iss saaray nizaam ki har cheez aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye chal rahi hai aur Allah hi iss saaray kaam ki tadbeer farma raha hai woh nishanain khol khol kar bayan karta hai, shayad ke tum apne rab ki mulaqaat ka yaqeen karo"
13,3,"aur wohi hai jis ne yeh zameen phela rakhi hai, is mein pahoron ke khontay garh rakhay hain aur darya baha diye hain usi ne har terhan ke phalon ke jore peda kiye hain, aur wohi din par raat taari karta hai un saari cheezon mein barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar se kaam letay hain"
13,4,"aur dekho, zameen mein allag allag khittay paye jatay hain jo aik dosray se mut-tasil waqay hain angoor ke baagh hain, khityan hain, khajoor ke darakht hain jin mein se kuch akehray hain aur kuch dohray sab ko aik hi pani sairaab karta hai magar mazay mein hum kisi ko behtar bana dete hain aur kisi ko kamtar un sab cheezon mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain"
13,5,"ab agar tumhe taajjub karna hai to taajjub ke qabil logon ka yeh qoul hai ke"" jab hum mar kar matti ho jayen ge to kya hum naye suray se peda kiye jayen ge ?"" yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne rab se kufar kya hai yeh woh log hain jin ki gardnon mein taoq parre hue hain yeh jahanumi hain aur jahannum mein hamesha rahen ge"
